headline: Accenture CEO Julie Sweet says Fortune 500s can survive AI—but they have to be willing to reinvent themselves top to bottom
summary: The Accenture CEO—who oversees 770,000 employees and counsels more Fortune 500 chiefs than almost anyone—shares lessons on AI adoption, career pivots, and resilience from her own battles with cancer.
